- VNOI Wiki — *Hash xâu*: <https://wiki.vnoi.info/algo/string/string-hashing>
- CP-Algorithms — *String Hashing*: <https://cp-algorithms.com/string/string-hashing.html>
- USACO Guide Plat — *String Hashing*: <https://usaco.guide/plat/string-hashing>
- Codeforces Blog — *Anti-Hash Test*: <https://codeforces.com/blog/entry/60442>
